---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services - Zero Fluff"
  description="AI implementation services for small businesses. No jargon, just practical solutions that work."
>
  <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h1>What I Do</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted">
        I take real business processes and make them faster, cheaper, and less painful
        with AI. Not as a concept. As a working thing you can use tomorrow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Core Offering -->
  <section class="section reveal" style="background-color: var(--color-border);">
    <div class="container narrow stack">
      <h2>Practical AI Implementation</h2>
      <p>
        Most AI consultants sell you a strategy. I build you a system. The difference
        matters: you end up with something that actually runs, not a document that
        sits in a drawer.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work with small businesses to find the tasks that eat up time -- the repetitive
        stuff, the manual data shuffling, the processes that make your team groan -- and
        I automate them. Using tools like N8N for workflow automation, custom AI integrations,
        and whatever else fits the job.
      </p>
      <p>
        This isn't about replacing people. It's about freeing them up to do the work
        that actually needs a human brain. I also make sure your team knows how to use
        what I've built, so it doesn't become another piece of abandoned software.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: How I Work -->
  <section class="section reveal">
    <div class="container stack-lg">
      <div class="narrow stack">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Three steps. No twelve-month roadmaps, no discovery phases that cost
          more than the actual work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>1. We Talk</h3>
          <p>
            I learn how your business works. Where time gets wasted, what
            frustrates your team, and where AI can make a genuine difference.
            This is a conversation, not a questionnaire.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>2. I Build</h3>
          <p>
            I create a working automation or AI tool tailored to your specific
            problem. You see real progress quickly -- not a strategy deck, but
            software that runs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card stack">
          <h3>3. You Use It</h3>
          <p>
            I hand it over with proper training so your team can actually use it.
            No mysterious black box. You understand what it does, how it works,
            and how to get the most out of it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: CTA -->
  <CTA />
</BaseLayout>
